---
title: "_onAuctionEnd (BaseAuction)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_check_fee_agg: hasFeeAggregator?
    q_check_fee_agg --> q_check_asset_bal: hasFeeAggregator == true
    q_check_asset_bal --> q_return_asset: assetBalance > 0
    q_return_asset --> q_check_out_bal: safeTransfer(asset, feeAggregator, assetBalance)
    q_check_asset_bal --> q_check_out_bal: assetBalance == 0
    q_check_fee_agg --> q_check_out_bal: hasFeeAggregator == false
    q_check_out_bal --> q_transfer_out: assetOutBalance > 0
    q_transfer_out --> [*]: safeTransfer(assetOut, assetOutReceiver, assetOutBalance)
    q_check_out_bal --> [*]: assetOutBalance == 0

    note right of q_return_asset
        INV-001: Remaining auctioned asset is returned to feeAggregator
        INV-002: Accumulated assetOut is forwarded to assetOutReceiver
    end note
